{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775887508913,"sessionID":"ses_284dc67edffeQA8vXFiu99qzyB","part":{"id":"prt_d7b24a90c001Vnj8uA1nQW47Vl","messageID":"msg_d7b24a028001ljBRJE6xSXz3pt","sessionID":"ses_284dc67edffeQA8vXFiu99qzyB","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_8105cd39775f4de7bd765dc9","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-043 — Architecture Design Documents & API Documentation\n\n- **AR ID**: AR-043\n- **Module**: docs\n- **Language**: Markdown\n- **Size**: M\n- **Status**: ST-3 Completed (tasks.md creation)\n\n## Pre-check\n\n- [ ] Verify existing architecture.md at `docs/docs/guides/architecture.md`\n- [ ] Verify existing API docs at `docs/docs/api/agent-runtime.md`\n- [ ] Verify existing CLI docs at `docs/docs/api/cli.md`\n\n---\n\n## Tasks\n\n### Phase 1: Architecture Design Document\n\n- [ ] **T-001**: Review and enhance existing `docs/docs/guides/architecture.md`\n  - Verify high-level system diagram includes all core components\n  - Verify core components documented (Agent Runtime, Code Interpreter, Router, Workload Manager)\n  - Verify Kubernetes deployment topology is covered\n  - Verify Helm chart structure documented\n\n### Phase 2: SDK Client API Documentation\n\n- [ ] **T-002**: Document ControlPlaneClient class\n  - Document `__init__` method with parameters (workload_manager_url, auth_token, timeout, etc.)\n  - Document `create_session` method with request/response schema\n  - Document `delete_session` method\n  - Document `close` method\n\n### Phase 3: REST API Documentation\n\n- [ ] **T-003**: Document Workload Manager `/v1/code-interpreter` endpoint\n  - Document POST `/v1/code-interpreter` (create session)\n  - Document DELETE `/v1/code-interpreter/{session_id}` (delete session)\n  - Include request/response schemas\n  - Include error codes and HTTP status codes\n\n### Phase 4: CRD Documentation\n\n- [ ] **T-004**: Document AgentRuntime CRD schema\n  - Create `docs/docs/api/crd-agentruntime.md`\n  - Document spec fields: maxSessionDuration, sessionTimeout, targetPorts, podTemplate\n  - Document status fields: conditions, observedGeneration, phase, endpoint\n  - Include YAML examples\n\n- [ ] **T-005**: Document CodeInterpreter CRD schema\n  - Create `docs/docs/api/crd-codeinterpreter.md`\n  - Document spec fields: authMode, maxSessionDuration, sessionTimeout, ports, template, warmPoolSize\n  - Document status fields: conditions, observedGeneration, ready, phase, endpoint\n  - Include YAML examples\n\n### Phase 5: Helm Values Documentation\n\n- [ ] **T-006**: Document Helm chart values\n  - Create `docs/docs/guides/helm-values.md` or add to existing configuration doc\n  - Document global values (namespace, image registry, etc.)\n  - Document router deployment values\n  - Document agentd controller values\n  - Document workload-manager values\n  - Document RBAC values\n  - Document CRD values\n  - Include default values and descriptions\n\n---\n\n## Verification Commands\n\n```bash\n# Verify docs structure\nls -la docs/docs/\nls -la docs/docs/api/\nls -la docs/docs/guides/\n\n# Verify architecture.md exists\ntest -f docs/docs/guides/architecture.md && echo \"EXISTS\" || echo \"MISSING\"\n\n# Verify API docs exist\ntest -f docs/docs/api/agent-runtime.md && echo \"agent-runtime EXISTS\" || echo \"MISSING\"\ntest -f docs/docs/api/code-interpreter.md && echo \"code-interpreter EXISTS\" || echo \"MISSING\"\ntest -f docs/docs/api/cli.md && echo \"cli EXISTS\" || echo \"MISSING\"\n\n# Verify new CRD docs (expected after tasks)\ntest -f docs/docs/api/crd-agentruntime.md && echo \"crd-agentruntime EXISTS\" || echo \"MISSING\"\ntest -f docs/docs/api/crd-codeinterpreter.md && echo \"crd-codeinterpreter EXISTS\" || echo \"MISSING\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- T-002 requires access to `agentcube/clients/control_plane.py` source code\n- T-004 requires access to `manifests/agentcube/templates/crd-agentruntime.yaml`\n- T-005 requires access to `manifests/agentcube/templates/crd-codeinterpreter.yaml`\n- T-006 requires access to `manifests/agentcube/values.yaml`\n\n---\n\n*Stage ST-3 completed*","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-043/tasks.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/manifests/agentcube/templates/crd-agentruntime.yaml\">\nERROR [1:3] Block collections are not allowed within flow collections\nERROR [1:5] Missing , or : between flow map items\nERROR [4:1] Unexpected flow-map-start at node end\nERROR [4:2] Unexpected flow-map-start at node end\nERROR [4:3] Unexpected seq-item-ind at node end\nERROR [4:5] Unexpected scalar at node end\nERROR [4:29] Unexpected flow-map-end token in YAML stream: \"}\"\nERROR [4:30] Unexpected flow-map-end token in YAML stream: \"}\"\nERROR [5:1] Unexpected scalar token in YAML stream: \"apiVersion\"\nERROR [5:11] Unexpected map-value-ind token in YAML stream: \":\"\nERROR [5:13] Unexpected scalar token in YAML stream: \"apiextensions.k8s.io/v1\"\nERROR [6:1] Unexpected scalar token in YAML stream: \"kind\"\nERROR [6:5] Unexpected map-value-ind token in YAML stream: \":\"\nERROR [6:7] Unexpected scalar token in YAML stream: \"CustomResourceDefinition\"\nERROR [7:1] Unexpected scalar token in YAML stream: \"metadata\"\nERROR [7:9] Unexpected map-value-ind token in YAML stream: \":\"\nERROR [8:3] Unexpected scalar token in YAML stream: \"name\"\nERROR [8:7] Unexpected map-value-ind token in YAML stream: \":\"\nERROR [8:9] Unexpected scalar token in YAML stream: \"agentruntimes.runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"\nERROR [9:3] Unexpected scalar token in YAML stream: \"annotations\"\n... and 346 more\n</diagnostics>\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/manifests/a